description: Creates the specified Data Lake Analytics account. This supplies the user with computation services for Data Lake Analytics workloads.

parameters.description: Parameters supplied to create a new Data Lake Analytics account.

properties.description: The Data Lake Analytics account properties to use for creating.

subscription_id.description: Get subscription credentials which uniquely identify Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the Azure resource group.

account_name.description: The name of the Data Lake Analytics account.
